item.description:

my compiler:

@echo off Title Compiler "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_12\bin\javac.exe" *.java pause

dont forget to change:

"C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_12\bin\javac.exe"

to ur version, like if u have version 06 u must change to:

"C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_06\bin\javac.exe"

and plz tell any errors u have when u compile
